tachyon.client.file

Class URIStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.client.file.URIStatus

  • @PublicApi
public class URIStatus
extends Object
    Wrapper around FileInfo. Represents the metadata about a file or directory in Tachyon. This is a snapshot of information about the file or directory and not all attributes are guaranteed to be up to date. Attributes documented as immutable will always be accurate, and attributes documented as mutable may be out of date.
